ts both maser and gyrosynchrotron radiation,\npotentially originating from substantially different locations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2013 21:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Mar 2013 14:32:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-08"}
