at 3T MR has a role in gynecologic\nbrachytherapy. These novel developments improve targeted treatment to the tumor\nwhile sparing the normal tissues.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Jan 2013 16:52:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-24"}
